Package com.intellij.diff.fragments

Interface LineFragment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DiffFragment
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LineFragmentImpl

    public interface LineFragment
extends DiffFragment
    Modified part of the text Offset ranges cover whole line, including '\n' at the end. But '\n' can be absent for the last line.
